<p source="SHANGBO.ZHENGZIJIAWANG 7.40.1 (STRIPS A1-A2) MACHENGYUAN 7: 173-174 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.1">鄭子家亡,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.2">邊人來告.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.3">莊王就大夫</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.4">而與之言曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.5">“鄭子家殺其君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.6">不穀日欲以告大夫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.7">以邦之病【甲 1】以急.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.8">於今而後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-1a.9">楚邦思[=應]爲諸侯正.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHENGZIJIAWANG 7.40.2 (STRIPS A2-A3) MACHENGYUAN 7: 174-175 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.1">今鄭子家殺其君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.2">將保其恭炎以沒入地,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.3">如上帝鬼【甲 2】神以爲怒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.4">吾將何以答?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.5">雖邦之病,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.6">將必爲師.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.7">乃起師,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-2a.8">圍鄭三月.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHENGZIJIAWANG 7.40.3 (STRIPS A3-A5) MACHENGYUAN 7: 175-177 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.1">鄭人請其故,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.2">王命答之曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.3">“鄭子【甲 3】 家顚覆天下之禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.4">弗畏鬼神之不祥,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.5">戕賊其君.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.6">將必使子家毋以成名立於上,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-3a.7">而滅【甲 4】XX 於下.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZHENGZIJIAWANG 7.40.4 (STRIPS A5-A6) MACHENGYUAN 7: 177-178 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.1">鄭人命以子良爲質.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.2">命使子家梨木三寸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.3">疏索以紘,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.4">毋敢當門而出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.5">掩之城基.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.6">【甲 5】王許之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.7">師未還,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.8">晉人涉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.9">將救鄭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0069_tls_001-4a.10">王將還.</seg>
                </p>

